stories_text_raw:
As a user, I want to submit data with a specific submission ID and status, so that I can keep track of my submissions.

As a user, I want to view my submission history, so that I can see the details of my past submissions.

As a FABS user, I want to validate a pending submission by its ID, so that I can ensure the submission is processed correctly.

As a FABS user, I want to download a file associated with my submission by its ID, so that I can access the submitted data.

As an agency user, I want to submit data including additional flexfields, so that I can provide more contextual information with my submission.

As an agency user, I want to check the submission period, so that I can be aware of the timeframe for submitting my data.

As a developer, I want to log issues encountered during development, so that I can keep a record of problems for future reference.

As a developer, I want to implement improvements to the logging system, so that I can enhance tracking and debugging capabilities.

As a user testing manager, I want to schedule testing sessions for multiple users on a specific date, so that we can assess user experience and gather feedback.

As a user testing manager, I want to generate a summary report of user testing, so that I can evaluate the results and insights gained from the sessions.

As a broker, I want to upload and validate submissions, so that I can ensure all submissions are processed and compliant.

As a broker, I want to retrieve error messages related to submissions, so that I can address any issues that arise during the validation process.
